+/******************************************************************************
+ * vbd.c
+ * 
+ * XenLinux virtual block device driver (xvd).
+ * 
+ * Copyright (c) 2003-2004, Keir Fraser & Steve Hand
+ * Modifications by Mark A. Williamson are (c) Intel Research Cambridge
+ * Copyright (c) 2004-2005, Christian Limpach
